title: Everything you need to know about a ‘supermoon’ eclipse — in 60 seconds
text:
What exactly is a supermoon eclipse? (1:01) Stargazers get ready for a supermoon lunar eclipse this Sunday. The last time we caught a glimpse of one was in 1982. But what is a supermoon lunar eclipse? Dipti Kapadia explains. Photo: Getty Images
See: How to watch the rare supermoon eclipse this weekend
